# ── Contact form ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the contact form. Get your form ID from https://formspree.io.
# Do NOT commit your real ID here — copy this file to .env.local and fill it in.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=your_formspree_form_id

# ── GitHub Pages deployment ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set to "true" only when building for GitHub Pages (adds /<repoName> basePath).
# Leave unset for local dev and Vercel/Netlify.
# GITHUB_PAGES=true
